{
  "stem": "12674.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was his relaxation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father had was born with a very beautiful tenor voice, a lyric tenor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had a very beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, of course, his parents were in no condition to afford anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When they had a birthday, they got a soft boiled egg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was a sign that there was a birthday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's what their present.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He told me that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And so when he was able to do this for himself, he went and took singing lessons to develop his voice.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was-- he came from a religious family and he was, you know, involved with religion in prayer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he became a chazzan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he was a cantor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was in Innsbruck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was there for the high holy days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And every year he would go there for the high holy days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was his-- between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur, that was his vacation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "As, you know, a fellow, that's what he was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He would go be a little bit mountain climbing and live there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But he felt that the food that was being served to him wasn't as what he was used to from home, because one of my grandmother's sisters, the youngest, her name was Nina, had in her youth been a cook in the home of Count Esterhazy, who was a very famous Austrian nobleman.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she could take two pieces of paper and make a banquet out of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So we ate the most fantastic food when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when I was older and I went to some restaurants in New York where the food costs more than somebody's salary.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
